>業</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">價</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">值，對</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">集</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">團</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">未</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">來</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">可</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">持</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">續</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">發</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">展</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">具</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">有</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">積</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">極</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">且</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">重</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">大</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">意</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">義。</span></p>   </div>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"hkej_hkex_notice_dl_btn_2014\">\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2025/0824/2025082400056_c.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">下載港交所通告原文</a>\n</div>\n        ",
